gn=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When EQ2 comes out what will happen?</span><hr size=1> Yeah I am not sure now if they are gonna make a EQ2. They are just gonna keep adding content with expansions and patches. I think it is a huge mistake on Verants part. The older areas of the world become trivialised as they add the new content and unless they go back and completely redesign the older areas they are now wasted space. Maybe CT was the first step to doing this.<br>
<br>
But even worse is the fact EQ is pretty much broke. They expanded the power base to much. Items went from a nice level of power to insane. In the old world the black enameled BP was a great piece of armor. Now it is trash and noone would wear it but some lucky noob in Innothule who is given it. The mobs who were once tough and fun to fight are now looked upon as easy. Vox, Naggy, they hit hard for their day but a person could actually tank them for more then 2 seconds. The fact a warrior with defensive still needs multiple clerics chaining CH just to keep him alive is IMO retarded. Other ways to make fights tough (and not dumbass ideas like Ali's AoE) should have been thought up. Lots of guards for uber mobs that act as pets, dungeons where certain mobs wander and the instant they see a raiding party call a alarm, maybe a dragon who actually flies into the air and breaths fire at the raid for a while from out of range of the melee (casters could still hit him and heal but they would then piss him off and guess who he is going after when he comes down) Hell even a default smart mob that goes after healers first, I know you all out there are saying OMG no! how would we win? But what do we do when we fight melee and healers, we kill the healers first. Give the mobs some AI and this game would work alot different.<br>
<br>
EQ is broke, If they dont make EQ2 then they might as well throw in the towl, some day a game will come out that will own EQ and cause it to die, they can make that EQ2 or leave that chance to another company. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senior Member</span><br>  Posts: 908<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/25/02 12:42 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/flappy.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When EQ2 comes out what will happen?</span><hr size=1> EQ2 will be announced at this spring's E3.<br>
